1. Mi smo *izabrali* najbolji restoran u gradu. (We have *chosen* the best restaurant in the city.)
2. Kada budete *izabrali* novu kameru, javite mi koju ste odabrali. (When you *select* a new camera, let me know which one you have chosen.)
3. Oni su već *izabrali* novog predsednika kluba. (They have already *elected* a new president of the club.)
4. Ko će *izabrati* najboljeg sportistu ove godine? (Who will *pick* the best athlete of the year?)
5. Kada budemo *izabrali* nove članove tima, obavestićemo vas. (When we *choose* new team members, we will inform you.)
6. Većina ljudi će *izabrati* vikend putovanje u prirodu umesto gradskog provoda. (Most people will *opt for* a weekend trip to nature instead of a city party.)
7. Oni su *izabrali* da žive u mirnom selu umesto u gradu. (They *decided* to live in a peaceful village instead of a city.)
8. Da li ste već *izabrali* odevnu kombinaciju za sutra? (Have you already *picked* out your outfit for tomorrow?)
9. Ovaj put su *izabrali* drugačiji pristup rešavanju problema. (This time they *selected* a different approach to solving the problem.)
10. Kada bih mogao *izabrati* bilo koju zemlju u kojoj želim da živim, izabrao bih Novi Zeland. (If I could *choose* any country I want to live in, I would choose New Zealand.)